snippet.title: Diana teaches baby Oliver | Developmental Games for a 1+ Year Old
snippet.description:
Diana is doing her homework. But little Oliver also wants to study. Diana decides to teach Oliver about shapes, colors, animal names and numbers. Fun educational games for children from 1 year old! Baby Oliver plays and develops at the same time!
Thanks for watching!
